g \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00e2n binh Ronaldo?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/052147-1.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Emre Can sau khi si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 30 tu\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d th\u00e0nh Turin</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m, h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro/m\u00f9a.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emre Can n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Emre Can n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/052147-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1c C\u0110V m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean anh trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh Turin t\u1eeb Liverpool theo d\u1ea1ng t\u1ef1 do, nh\u01b0ng Emre Can m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 hoan ngh\u00eanh v\u00e0 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i CR7:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nh\u01b0ng Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh n\u00ean c\u1ea3 k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Juventus ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u01b0 \u2018h\u1ed5 m\u1ecdc th\u00eam c\u00e1nh\u2019. T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 CR7.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ronaldo kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 quen thu\u1ed9c \u1edf Juventus v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean IC Cup t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, khi g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bayern Munich, Benfica, MLS All-Stars v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (ng\u00e0y 4/8).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-mat-juventus-176-191385.html\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Juventus, Cristiano Ronaldo n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ra m\u1eaft Juventus v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1327","checkdouble":"191387"},{"date":"05:50 17/07","title":"Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/man-utd-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-cau-thu-tiep-theo-sau-4-nam-gan-bo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn r\u1eddi Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ajax Amsterdam trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb l\u00e2u khi trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m nay \u1edf Old Trafford k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, Daley Blind kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng, v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 7 tr\u1eadn thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf Premier League (3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh)</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind r\u1eddi MU tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ajax Amsterdam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind r\u1eddi MU tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ajax Amsterdam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/15/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c: H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind r\u1eddi MU tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ajax Amsterdam sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. N\u1eafm l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay Man Utd \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Ajax Amsterdam, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1eeb thu\u1edf nh\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2014.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, MU v\u00e0 Ajax \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u201cg\u1eedi tr\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d n\u00e0y, c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e3 giao d\u1ecbch \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1m ph\u00e1t. Blind tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Amsterdam v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 70.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Daley Blind n\u1ed5i l\u00ean t\u1eeb k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014 \u1edf Brazil khi l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap H\u00e0 Lan c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 ba chung cu\u1ed9c. Ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, anh theo ch\u00e2n \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Louis Van Gaal c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 cho Blind khi Van Gaal ra \u0111i sau hai n\u0103m v\u00e0 thay th\u1ebf b\u1eb1ng Mourinho. \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t\u201d v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4ng minh, \u0111\u1ea7u \u00f3c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Blind kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf 141 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00e0nh c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA Cup, League Cup, Si\u00eau C\u00fap Anh v\u00e0 Europa League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/15/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/99-blind-roi-mu-o-he-2018-172-191360.html\">99% c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018?</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Daley Blind r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1326","checkdouble":"191388"},{"date":"06:17 17/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/huyen-thoai-duc-danh-gia-nhung-thu-mon-xuat-sac-nhat-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Oliver Kahn v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i Hugo Lloris, Thibaut Courtois, Danijel Subasic v\u00e0 Jordan Pickford sau m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n vinh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00e0nh cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u00f3i d\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 63/64 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, c\u1ea3 32 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u ghi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t hai b\u00e0n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ghi nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sau c\u00e1c n\u0103m 1998 v\u00e0 2014.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Oliver Kahn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Oliver Kahn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/4-ly-do-de-tin-DT-Anh-vo-dich-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Oliver Kahn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc trong l\u00f2ng gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong khung g\u1ed7. Ch\u00ednh th\u1ebf m\u00e0 Oliver Kahn, ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng l\u1eabn Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup 2002, \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ra nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, bao g\u1ed3m ch\u00ednh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Ph\u00e1p, B\u1ec9, Croatia v\u00e0 Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cHugo Lloris l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f4i tay, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao r\u1ea5t ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cThibaut Courtois th\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t 1v1 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n. Danijel Subasic \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1eaft penalty thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Jordan Pickford b\u1edfi c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 non kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u1ea3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m85 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n n\u1eefa, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi n\u1ebfu kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khai th\u00e1c tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i chung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/benjamin-pavard-va-nhung-cai-ten-hoa-rong-sau-vck-world-cup-2018-421-191374.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/benjamin-pavard-va-nhung-cai-ten-hoa-rong-sau-vck-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/benjamin-pavard-va-nhung-cai-ten-hoa-rong-sau-vck-world-cup-2018-421-191374.html\">Benjamin Pavard v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean h\u00f3a r\u1ed3ng sau VCK World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed7i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft EURO hay World Cup lu\u00f4n gi\u00fap l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1. V\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1325","checkdouble":"191389"},{"date":"06:24 17/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (17/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1772018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !impor