\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/phap-vs-croatia-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-463-191254.html\" target=\"_blank\">Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-2 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</span>, Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/dt-phap-tai-world-cup-2018-van-de-chung-toc-chua-the-lam-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi d\u00e0n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c l\u1ee9a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 k\u1ebf c\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t, G\u00e0 Tr\u1ed1ng Gaulouis \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Lothar Matthaus c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 tin khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1edbi trong tay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o th\u1ebf v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t ngay trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00e3 qua, Les Bleus c\u0169ng v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 Dejan Lovren.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-ngoa-ngoat-dap-tra-hazard-va-courtois-tuong-chelsea-cua-may-nguoi-la-barca-chac-421-191190.html\">Griezmann ngoa ngo\u1eaft \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 Hazard v\u00e0 Courtois: T\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea c\u1ee7a m\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 Barca ch\u1eafc?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-ranh-gioi-giua-binh-thuong-va-bat-thuong-421-191341.html\">Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: Ranh gi\u1edbi gi\u1eefa b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-an-tuong-khong-the-dong-dem-421-191297.html\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018: \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-gianh-cup-vang-thuyet-phuc-chinh-phuc-the-gioi-bang-tinh-than-mayweather-421-191322.html\">Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c: Chinh ph\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng tinh th\u1ea7n Mayweather</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1323","checkdouble":"191391"},{"date":"06:54 17/07","title":"T\u00e2m th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Conte g\u1eedi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/tam-thu-cua-conte-gui-chelsea-sau-khi-bi-sa-thai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd chia tay s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge sau hai n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Maurizio Sarri, mang v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng th\u00eam hai danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2m th\u01b0 Conte g\u1eedi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2m th\u01b0 Conte g\u1eedi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-Conte-da-bi-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2m th\u01b0 Conte g\u1eedi Chelsea sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf CLB b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Chelsea v\u00ec n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u00ec t\u00f4i trong su\u1ed1t hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 qua. Ch\u00ednh nh\u1edd m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup.\u201d</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cG\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng chung c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n h\u1ecd v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o cho t\u00f4i khi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cG\u1eedi t\u1edbi c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1eadn t\u1ee5y v\u00ec c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00ec tinh th\u1ea7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh su\u1ed1t hai n\u0103m v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng, \u0111am m\u00ea b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd m\u00e3i n\u1eb1m trong tr\u00e1i tim t\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i xin ch\u00fac cho Chelsea v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i ra \u0111i v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd nh\u1ea5t t\u1eebng chia s\u1ebb c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n, v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd theo t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ch\u1eb7ng h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u1eed th\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp theo trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1322","checkdouble":"191393"},{"date":"15:44 16/07","title":"Kaka l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Los Blancos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 suy t\u00ednh k\u1ef9 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u1edbi k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus theo th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho t\u1edbi l\u00fac ra \u0111i, Ronaldo v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real v\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n sau 44 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng theo g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u Galatico: Kaka th\u00ec CR7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 h\u01a1n ai h\u1ebft \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/Kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-Ronaldo-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Cristiano l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real tr\u00ean Omnisport. \u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Madrid sang Juventus l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd th\u1ee9c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCristiano bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ra \u0111i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng: \u2018T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Real v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c\u2019. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Juve \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha sang Italia ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng.\u201d <br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo v\u00e0 d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Kaka cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 nh\u01b0 Ronaldo. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t hay kh\u00f4ng, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil n\u00f3i th\u00eam:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" title=\"Ronaldo va Kaka\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Kaka khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00fang l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Cristiano th\u00f4ng qua nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t may m\u1eafn v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi. C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u0169ng may m\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y c\u00f9ng anh \u1ea5y trong 4 n\u0103m.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y Cristiano chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1edbi m\u1ee9c n\u00e0o, gi\u00e0u kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd ra sao. Anh \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Cristiano s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/spalletti-so-sanh-perisic-voi-ronaldo-421-191163.html\">Sao Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/tay-ban-nha-doa-bat-ronaldo-tai-italia-188-191161.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ecda b\u1eaft Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rodrigo-ve-thay-ronaldo-180-191111.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u1ec1 thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1321","checkdouble":"191352"},{"date":"17:28 16/07","title":"H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/he-lo-2-tan-binh-tiep-theo-se-duoc-barca-cong-bo-trong-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho bi\u1ebft CLB Barca s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng hai t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet.</h2><h2>Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Willian v\u00e0&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Adrien Rabiot</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian roi san nhuong vi tri cho Firmino\" title=\"Willian r\u1eddi s\u00e2n nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Firmino\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/willian.JPG\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Barca s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t v\u1ee5 Willian ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">World Cup 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fac th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u1edbi Barcelona, sau c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo t\u1edd Don Balon, CLB Barcelona \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i r\u1ea5t kh\u1ea9n tr\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam hai t\u00e2n binh trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Chelsea Willian v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf trung t\u00e2m tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 PSG, Adrien Rabiot.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Willian, Barca \u0111ang t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Chelsea khi ch\u1ed3ng l\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Barca c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot t\u1eeb PSG. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Rabiot gia nh\u1eadp Blaugrana v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u euro.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Paul Pogba, theo t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo cho hay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba - Mino Raiola \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barcelona v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalan ngay trong H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Hi\u1ec7n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Manchester. Ph\u00eda M.U c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1320","checkdouble":"191356"},{"date":"16:49 16/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u World Cup 2018: Vinh danh Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/doi-hinh-tieu-bieu-world-cup-2018-vinh-danh-ngoai-hang-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f