 href=\"/bong-da-italia/muon-oai-ronaldo-juventus-tinh-tai-hop-pogba-176-191121.html\">M\u01b0\u1ee3n oai Ronaldo, Juventus t\u00ednh t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kevin-strootman-khong-ngai-doi-dau-ronaldo-tai-serie-a-176-191088.html\">Sao Roma kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1319","checkdouble":"191358"},{"date":"16:26 16/07","title":"S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 32: 3 v\u0129 nh\u00e2n \u201c\u0111a di n\u0103ng\u201d t\u1eebng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/song-cung-world-cup-2018-so-32-3-vi-nhan-da-di-nang-tung-len-dinh-the-gioi.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u00e0nh cho \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Deschamps c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 2 c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ai? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 qua S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 32.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 32:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ygJNwowraAQ\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau 20 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n. L\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, ch\u1ec9 25 tu\u1ed5i 10 th\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HLV Didier Deschamps, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 Kylian Mbappe, Paul Pogba, Benjamin Pavard hay Lucas Hernandez\u2026 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft \u0111en qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y Les Bleus \u0111\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 49 tu\u1ed5i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi ri\u00eang Deschamps, ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 20 n\u0103m, ch\u00ednh \u00f4ng t\u1eebng mang b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Deschamps th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u00d4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 3 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3 HLV l\u1eabn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, nh\u1eefng Mario Zagallo (Brazil) v\u00e0 Franz Beckenbauer c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 3 v\u0129 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng theo d\u00f5i Clip S\u1ed1ng c\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 s\u1ed1 32 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, h\u00e3y truy c\u1eadp Bongda24h.vn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nh\u1eefng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u00e9!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong><br />\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1318","checkdouble":"191359"},{"date":"16:42 16/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/nhung-hinh-anh-dau-tien-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-toi-juventus-kiem-tra-y-te.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class=